reviews.name: RWS Super Hollow Point .22 Pellets, 250 Count
reviews.reviewText:
Great product, hard hitting pellet with the best expansion. I have used other pellets
and I found these to be the best in accuracy and hitting power.
reviews.title: Great product

reviews.name: RWS Super Hollow Point .22 Pellets, 250 Count
reviews.reviewText: Superbly made pellets with great accuracy and very tight groupings out of my Benjamin Titan pretty much one whole.
reviews.title: Great Accuracy

reviews.name: RWS Super Hollow Point .22 Pellets, 250 Count
reviews.reviewText: Absolutely the most consistently accurate projectile I have found. I have a stoeger 20x and it can hit a 1" bullseye consistently at 35yd. This pellet will also penetrate thru a 1/4" wood lath stake at 85yds!!! No wonder it's the best seller. RWS knows what they're doing with this design.
reviews.title: This pellet ROCKS!
